# Stack Overview

- Framework: Next.js (App Router) + TypeScript + React
- UI: Shadcn + Tailwind CSS
- Data storage: MongoDB Atlas + Prisma ORM
- Auth: None
- Data fetching:
  - **Server-side:** Next.js Server Actions
- Data source:
  - Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis (FRED) API
- Deployment: Vercel
- Use `\src` directory for all app code and use the root for all config.
